					</div>
					
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
						<div class="space-y-4">
							<div class="bg-primary-900 border border-primary-700 p-4">
								<div class="flex items-start space-x-3 mb-2">
									<span class="text-tertiary-400 font-mono">âˆ‘</span>
